      • acquire

        public W acquire()
          throws InterruptedException

        Acquires a managed buffer from the pool. If the pool is empty, waits for a buffer to become available. The buffer has a lock count of one.

        Returns:
        the acquired buffer
        Throws:
        InterruptedException - if the current thread is interrupted
